reviewText:
Have this DVD and it's filled with tons of useful instructional materails & tehnic indeed.
Having someone like Malaipet that has fought close to 200 Pro. fights helps big time . He knows his Muay Thai for sure !

Dvd was a bit short, but entirely composed of useful material. Well explained. No filler. Should keep me busy for a while.
Seller was on point. Quick and easy transaction
